<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Julya Nail Designer | Estúdio de Luxo</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --skin-1: #f5ede6;
            --skin-2: #e8d5c4;
            --skin-3: #d4b5a0;
            --white:  #ffffff;
            --off-white: #faf8f6;
            --gold:   #c4984a;
            --gold-2: #d9ae6a;
            --gold-pale: #f0e0c8;
            --gray-1: #f0ecea;
            --gray-2: #b0a49e;
            --gray-3: #6b5f58;
            --ink:    #2a2220;
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }

        body {
            background: var(--off-white);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        nav {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            transition: background 0.5s, padding 0.4s, backdrop-filter 0.5s;
        }
        nav.scrolled {
            background: rgba(250,248,246,0.92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.15);
        }
        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--ink);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .nav-cta {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 8px 18px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .nav-cta:active { background: var(--gold); color: white; }

        #hero {
            min-height: 100svh;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--skin-1) 0%, var(--skin-2) 60%, var(--skin-3) 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding: 0 28px 56px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        #hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px; right: -80px;
            width: 320px; height: 320px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        #hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 80px; right: -40px;
            width: 200px; height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.3);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-monogram {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-45%, -52%);
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 55vw;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            line-height: 1;
            user-select: none;
            pointer-events: none;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
        }

        .hero-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.3s forwards;
        }
        .hero-tag::before {
            content: '';
            width: 28px; height: 1px;
            background: var(--gold);
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 14vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.0;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: var(--ink);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.5s forwards;
        }
        .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: var(--gray-3);
            line-height: 1.9;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.7s forwards;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.9s forwards;
        }
        .hero-btn-circle {
            width: 50px; height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--gold);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .hero-btn:active .hero-btn-circle { transform: scale(0.9); }

        .hero-scroll {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 56px; right: 28px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 1s 1.4s forwards;
        }
        .hero-scroll span {
            font-size: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gray-2);
            writing-mode: vertical-rl;
        }
        .scroll-bar {
            width: 1px; height: 44px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
            animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .marquee-band {
            background: var(--ink);
            padding: 14px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .marquee-inner {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: marquee 22s linear infinite;
        }
        .marquee-item {
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold-2);
            padding: 0 28px;
        }
        .marquee-sep {
            display: inline-block;
            color: var(--gold);
            opacity: 0.5;
            font-size: 0.5rem;
        }

        #servicos {
            padding: 72px 28px 60px;
            background: var(--white);
        }
        .sec-label {
            font-size: 0.58rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .sec-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--gold-pale); }

        .sec-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }
        .sec-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

        .services-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

        .service-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-1);
            padding: 22px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .service-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-1); }

        .service-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .service-num {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-style: italic;
            min-width: 28px;
        }
        .service-info { flex: 1; }
        .service-name {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .service-item.open .service-name,
        .service-item:active .service-name { color: var(--gold); }

        .service-price {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--gray-2);
            margin-top: 3px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .service-icon {
            width: 32px; height: 32px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.35s;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .service-item.open .service-icon {
            background: var(--gold);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--gold);
            transform: rotate(45deg);
        }
        .service-desc {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--gray-3);
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.3s;
            padding-left: 44px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .service-item.open .service-desc {
            max-height: 180px;
            padding-top: 12px;
        }

        .combos-section {
            margin-top: 70px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gold-pale);
            padding-top: 48px;
        }
        .combo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 28px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .combo-card {
            background: var(--off-white);
            border: 1px solid var(--gold-pale);
            padding: 24px 20px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .combo-card:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
        .combo-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--gold);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-size: 0.55rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .combo-name {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .combo-items {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--gray-3);
            margin: 14px 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .combo-price {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .combo-save {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-left: 8px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .highlights {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1px;
            background: var(--gray-1);
            margin-top: 1px;
        }
        .highlight-card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight-card:first-child {
            background: var(--skin-1);
        }
        .hl-num {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--gold);
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .hl-label {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gray-3);
            margin-top: 8px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        #form {
            padding: 72px 28px 80px;
            background: var(--ink);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        #form::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -120px; right: -80px;
            width: 360px; height: 360px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.1);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-size: 0.58rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold-2);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .form-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(196,152,74,0.2); }

        .form-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .form-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-2); }

        .form-sub {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 44px;
        }

        .field { margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; }
        .field label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.55rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .field input,
        .field select,
        .field textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.2);
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: var(--white);
            font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            outline: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .field input:focus,
        .field select:focus,
        .field textarea:focus { border-bottom-color: var(--gold); }
        .field input::placeholder,
        .field textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
        .field select option { background: #2a2220; }
        .field textarea { resize: none; min-height: 72px; }

        .field.error input,
        .field.error select,
        .field.error textarea {
            border-bottom-color: #d9534f;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 0.55rem;
            color: #d9534f;
            margin-top: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .field-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }

        .btn-whatsapp {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px;
            background: var(--gold);
            border: none;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.15s;
            margin-top: 8px;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        .btn-whatsapp:active { background: var(--gold-2); transform: scale(0.98); }
        .btn-whatsapp svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

        footer {
            background: #181210;
            padding: 48px 28px 36px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,152,74,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: var(--gold-2);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer-tag {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .footer-divider {
            width: 40px;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--gold);
            opacity: 0.3;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
        }
        .footer-social {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 28px;
            margin: 24px 0 20px;
        }
        .footer-social a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .footer-social a:active { color: var(--gold-2); }
        .footer-social svg {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }
        .footer-map {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer-map a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .footer-map a:active { color: var(--gold-2); }
        .footer-map svg {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            visibility: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: visibility 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .modal-overlay.active {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .modal-container {
            background: var(--off-white);
            max-width: 440px;
            width: 85%;
            padding: 32px 28px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            transform: scale(0.96);
            transition: transform 0.25s;
        }
        .modal-overlay.active .modal-container {
            transform: scale(1);
        }
        .modal-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            color: var(--ink);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .modal-message {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--gray-3);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .modal-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .modal-btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 10px 22px;
            font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            color: var(--ink);
        }
        .modal-btn-primary {
            background: var(--gold);
            border-color: var(--gold);
            color: var(--ink);
        }
        .modal-btn-primary:active { background: var(--gold-2); transform: scale(0.96); }
        .modal-btn:active { transform: scale(0.96); }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes marquee {
            from { transform: translateX(0); }
            to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
        }
        @keyframes scrollPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scaleY(0.6); transform-origin: top; }
            50%       { opacity: 1;   transform: scaleY(1); }
        }

        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
        }
        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 28px 60px; }
            nav.scrolled { padding: 18px 60px; }
            #hero {
                padding: 0 80px 80px;
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: flex-end;
            }
            .hero-title { font-size: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6.5rem); }
            .hero-monogram { font-size: 45vw; }
            #servicos { padding: 100px 80px; }
            #form { padding: 100px 80px; }
            .form-inner-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 80px;
                align-items: start;
            }
            footer { padding: 64px 80px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav id="navbar">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">JND</a>
    <a href="#form" class="nav-cta">Agendar</a>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-monogram">J</div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-tag">Estúdio de Luxo</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Julya<br><em>Nail</em><br>Designer</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">A excelência em cada detalhe das suas unhas. Uma experiência criada só para você.</p>
        <a href="#form" class="hero-btn">
            <div class="hero-btn-circle">→</div>
            Agendar Agora
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">
        <span>Scroll</span>
        <div class="scroll-bar"></div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="marquee-band" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-inner" id="marqueeInner"></div>
</div>

<section id="servicos">
    <div class="sec-label">O que oferecemos</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Nossos<br><em>Serviços</em></h2>
    <div class="services-list" id="servicesList"></div>
    <div class="combos-section" id="combosSection"></div>
    <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.7rem; text-align: center; color: var(--gray-2); font-style: italic;">Todos os procedimentos de unhas incluem cutilagem.</div>
</section>

<div class="highlights">
    <div class="highlight-card reveal">
        <div class="hl-num">9+</div>
        <div class="hl-label">Serviços<br>Exclusivos</div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight-card reveal">
        <div class="hl-num">100%</div>
        <div class="hl-label">Produtos<br>Premium</div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight-card reveal">
        <div class="hl-num">15d</div>
        <div class="hl-label">Durabilidade<br>Garantida</div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight-card reveal">
        <div class="hl-num">★★★</div>
        <div class="hl-label">Atendimento<br>Luxo</div>
    </div>
</div>

<section id="form">
    <div class="form-inner-grid">
        <div class="form-head reveal">
            <div class="form-label">Agendamento</div>
            <h2 class="form-title">Reserve<br>seu <em>Momento</em></h2>
            <p class="form-sub">Atendimento exclusivo mediante agendamento. Confirmamos via WhatsApp em até 24h.</p>
        </div>

        <form id="appointmentForm">
            <div class="field reveal" data-field="name">
                <label>Nome Completo</label>
